text: Waleska Amaya (born 2 April 1986) is a Honduran footballer who currently plays as a midfielder. ==Career== Amaya plays football for Universidad in San Pedro Sula's local women's football league. Amaya is a member of the Honduras women's national football team. She scored a goal in a 2015 FIFA Women's World Cup qualifying match against Belize. ==References== == External links == * Category:1986 births Category:Living people Category:Honduran women's footballers Category:Women's association football midfielders Category:Honduras women's international footballers
